### Orders — multipart ingest, paginated list, single detail
###
### Run "Login" first. File-upload requests reference the committed sample
### orders at samples/orders/ via REST Client's `< path` directive.

@host = http://localhost:8000

# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123


# ============================================================================
# POST /api/orders — multipart upload (one block per format)
# ============================================================================

### JSON (Carrefour-style)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-json.json"
Content-Type: application/json

< ../../../samples/orders/sample-json.json
--ROT--

###

### XML (Facturae-flavoured PO schema)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-xml-facturae.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

< ../../../samples/orders/sample-xml-facturae.xml
--ROT--

###

### CSV (Leroy Merlin multi-row export)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-csv.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ../../../samples/orders/sample-csv.csv
--ROT--

###

### EDIFACT D.96A ORDERS
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-edifact-carrefour.edi"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ../../../samples/orders/sample-edifact-carrefour.edi
--ROT--

###

### PDF (multimodal Parser Agent — costs ~$0.02 if Anthropic key is set)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-pdf.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../../samples/orders/sample-pdf.pdf
--ROT--

###

### Unsupported extension → 415
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ROT

--ROT
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="order.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

random bytes that no parser supports
--ROT--


# ============================================================================
# GET /api/orders — paginated list with optional filters
# ============================================================================

### All orders, page 1, default page_size=50
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Pending review only, smaller page
GET {{host}}/api/orders?status=pending_review&page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### By retailer
GET {{host}}/api/orders?retailer_code=CARREFOUR-ES&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### By supplier
GET {{host}}/api/orders?supplier_code=IBERIAN-FOODS&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}


# ============================================================================
# GET /api/orders/{id} — full detail
# ============================================================================
### Replace the UUID with one from the list above
GET {{host}}/api/orders/67e766c7-b1cf-4628-a3d0-ebf911330522
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
